指定者：
类 java.text.DateFormat 中的 format
参数：
date - The date to format into a string
toAppendTo - StringBuffer to which the formatted date will be appended
pos - Keeps track of the position of the field within the returned string. On input: an alignment field, if desired. On output: the offsets of the alignment field.Unsupported field positions are ignored.
